<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;b. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in connection with any ongoing or prospective legal proceedings;</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;c. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in order to establish, exercise or defend our legal rights (including

providing information to others for the purposes of fraud prevention

and reducing credit risk);</span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;d. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">to the purchaser (or prospective purchaser) of any business or asset

that we are (or are contemplating) selling; and</span></span></p>


<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;4.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Except as provided in this policy, we will not provide your personal information to third parties.</span></span></p>



<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">5. International data transfers</span></h2>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;5.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Information that we collect may be stored and processed in and transferred between any of the countries in which we operate in order to enable us to use the information in accordance with this policy.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;5.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Information that we collect may be transferred to the following countries which do not have data protection laws equivalent to those in force in the European Economic Area: the United States of America, Russia, Japan, China and India.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;5.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Personal information that you publish on our website, mobile website and mobile application or submit for publication on our website, mobile website and mobile application may be available, via the internet, around the world. We cannot prevent the use or misuse of such information by others.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;5.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You expressly agree to the transfers of personal information described in this Section 5.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">6. Retaining personal information</span></h2>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;6.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">This Section 6 sets out our data retention policies and procedure, which are designed to help ensure that we comply with our legal obligations in relation to the retention and deletion of personal information.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;6.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Personal information that we process for any purpose or purposes shall not be kept for longer than is necessary for that purpose or those purposes.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;6.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Without prejudice to Section 6.2, we will usually delete personal data falling within the categories set out below at the date/time set out below:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">profile information will be deleted within 24 hours of you deleting your account.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;6.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Notwithstanding the other provisions of this Section 6, we will retain documents (including electronic documents) containing personal data:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">to the extent that we are required to do so by law;</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;b. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">if we believe that the documents may be relevant to any ongoing or prospective legal proceedings; and</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;c. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in order to establish, exercise or defend our legal rights (including providing information to others for the purposes of fraud prevention and reducing credit risk).</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">7. Security of personal information</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;7.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We will take reasonable technical and organisational precautions to prevent the loss, misuse or alteration of your personal information.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;7.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We will store all the personal information you provide on our secure (password- and firewall-protected) servers.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;7.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">All electronic financial transactions entered into through our website will be protected by encryption technology.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;7.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You acknowledge that the transmission of information over the internet is inherently insecure, and we cannot guarantee the security of data sent over the internet.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;7.5 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You are responsible for keeping the password you use for accessing our website confidential; we will not ask you for your password (except when you log in to our website).</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">8. Amendments</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;8.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We may update this policy from time to time by publishing a new version on our website, mobile website and mobile application.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;8.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You should check this page occasionally to ensure you are happy with any changes to this policy.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;8.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We may notify you of changes to this policy by email or through the private messaging system on our website, mobile website and mobile application.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">9. Your rights</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;9.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You may instruct us to provide you with any personal information we hold about you; provision of such information will be subject to:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">the payment of a fee (currently fixed at GBP 12.99); and</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;b. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB"></span>the supply of appropriate evidence of your identity (for this purpose, we will usually accept a photocopy of your passport certified by a solicitor or bank plus an original copy of a utility bill showing your current address).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;9.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We may withhold personal information that you request to the extent permitted by law.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;9.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You may instruct us at any time not to process your personal information for marketing purposes.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;9.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">In practice, you will usually either expressly agree in advance to our use of your personal information for marketing purposes, or we will provide you with an opportunity to opt out of the use of your personal information for marketing purposes.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">10. Third party websites</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;10.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Our website, mobile website and mobile application includes hyperlinks to, and details of, third party websites.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;10.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We have no control over, and are not responsible for, the privacy policies and practices of third parties.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">11. Updating information</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;11.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Please let us know if the personal information that we hold about you needs to be corrected or updated.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">12. About cookies</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;12.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">A cookie is a file containing an identifier (a string of letters and numbers) that is sent by a web server to a web browser and is stored by the browser. The identifier is then sent back to the server each time the browser requests a page from the server.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;12.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Cookies may be either &quot;persistent&quot; cookies or &quot;session&quot; cookies: a persistent cookie will be stored by a web browser and will remain valid until its set expiry date, unless deleted by the user before the expiry date; a session cookie, on the other hand, will expire at the end of the user session, when the web browser is closed.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;12.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Cookies do not typically contain any information that personally identifies a user, but personal information that we store about you may be linked to the information stored in and obtained from cookies.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;12.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Cookies can be used by web servers to identify and track users as they navigate different pages on a website and identify users returning to a website.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;12.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Cookies can be used by web servers to identify and track users as they navigate different pages on a website and identify users returning to a website.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">13. Our cookies</span></h2>	
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;13.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We use both session and persistent cookies on our website.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;13.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">The names of the cookies that we use on our website, and the purposes for which they are used, are set out below:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">we use location cookie on our website to recognise a computer when a user visits the website / track users as they navigate the website / enable the use of a shopping cart on the website / improve the website&#39;s usability / analyse the use of the website / administer the website / prevent fraud and improve the security of the website / personalise the website for each user / target advertisements which may be of particular interest to specific users;</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">14. Analytics cookies</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;14.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">We use Google Analytics to analyse the use of our website.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;14.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Our analytics service provider generates statistical and other information about website use by means of cookies.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;14.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">The information generated relating to our website is used to create reports about the use of our website.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;14.4 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Our analytics service provider&#39;s privacy policy is available at: <a href="http://www.google.com/policies/privacy/" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/policies/privacy/.</a></span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">15. Third party cookies</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;15.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Our website also uses third party cookies.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;15.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">
    We publish Google AdSense interest-based advertisements on our website.
    
    These are tailored by Google to reflect your interests. To determine your
    
    interests, Google will track your behaviour on our website and on other
    
    websites across the web using the DoubleClick cookie. / We publish Google
    
    AdSense advertisements on our website. To determine your interests,
    
    Google will track your behaviour on our website and on other websites
    
    across the web using the DoubleClick cookie. This behaviour tracking allows
    
    Google to tailor the advertisements you see on other websites to reflect your
    
    interests (we do not publish interest-based advertisements on this
    
    website).] You can view, delete or add interest categories associated with
    
    your browser by visiting: <a href="http://www.google.com/settings/ads/" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/settings/ads/</a>. You can
    
    also opt out of the AdSense partner network cookie using those settings or
    
    using the NAI&#39;s (Network Advertising Initiative&#39;s) multi-cookie opt-out
    
    mechanism at:  <a href="http://www.networkadvertising.org/choices/" target="_blank">http://www.networkadvertising.org/choices/</a>. However, these
    
    opt-out mechanisms themselves use cookies, and if you clear the cookies
    
    from your browser your opt-out will not be maintained. To ensure that an
    
    opt-out is maintained in respect of a particular browser, you may wish to
    
    consider using the Google browser plug-in available at:
    
     <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads/plugin" target="_blank">https://www.google.com/settings/ads/plugin</a>.
</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">16. Blocking cookies</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;16.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Most browsers allow you to refuse to accept cookies; for example:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Internet Explorer (version 11) you can block cookies using the cookie handling override settings available by clicking &quot;Tools&quot;, &quot;Internet Options&quot;, &quot;Privacy&quot; and then &quot;Advanced&quot;;</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;b. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Firefox (version 39) you can block all cookies by clicking &quot;Tools&quot;, &quot;Options&quot;, &quot;Privacy&quot;, selecting &quot;Use custom settings for history&quot; from the drop-down menu, and unticking &quot;Accept cookies from sites&quot;; and</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;c. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Chrome (version 44), you can block all cookies by accessing the &quot;Customise and control&quot; menu, and clicking &quot;Settings&quot;, &quot;Show advanced settings&quot; and &quot;Content settings&quot;, and then selecting &quot;Block sites from setting any data&quot; under the &quot;Cookies&quot; heading.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;16.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Blocking all cookies will have a negative impact upon the usability of many websites.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;16.3 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">If you block cookies, you will not be able to use all the features on our website.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">17. Deleting cookies</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;17.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You can delete cookies already stored on your computer; for example:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;a. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Internet Explorer (version 11), you must manually delete cookie files (you can find instructions for doing so at <a href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/internet-explorer/delete-manage-cookies#ie=ie- 11);" target="_blank">http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/internet-explorer/delete-manage-cookies#ie=ie- 11);</a></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;b. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Firefox (version 39), you can delete cookies by clicking &quot;Tools&quot;, &quot;Options&quot; and &quot;Privacy&quot;, then selecting &quot;Use custom settings for history&quot; from the drop-down menu, clicking &quot;Show Cookies&quot;, and then clicking &quot;Remove All Cookies&quot;; and</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 28.35pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;c. </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">in Chrome (version 44), you can delete all cookies by accessing the &quot;Customise and control&quot; menu, and clicking &quot;Settings&quot;, &quot;Show advanced settings&quot; and &quot;Clear browsing data&quot;, and then selecting &quot;Cookies and other site and plug-in data&quot; before clicking &quot;Clear browsing data&quot;.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;17.2 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">Deleting cookies will have a negative impact on the usability of many websites.</span></span></p>

<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt;">18. Cookie preferences</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 14.15pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-GB">&nbsp;18.1 </span><!--[endif]--><span lang="EN-GB">You can manage your preferences relating to the use of cookies on our website by visiting your profile settings</span></span></p>

